dc_description_s: Prepared and published by the Defense Mapping Agency. Depths shown by isolines and soundings. Relief shown by contours, spot heights, and hachures. "From various sources to 1961." Antarctica, Riiser-Larsen Peninsula to West Ice Shelf (Raster Image). LandInfo.
